byline.contributor: Hussein Mohamed reported from Mogadishu, and Jeffrey Gettleman from Nairobi, Kenya.

lead_paragraph: The attack occurred hours after the country’s new president, Mohamed Abdullahi Mohamed, announced an offensive against the Shabab militant group.
